metadata.name: Nounish Toadz #1
metadata.description: Nounish Toadz is a collection of 400 glasses-wearing CrypToadz, living on the Ethereum blockchain. The goal of this project is to complement the original 352 *CrypToadz by Gremplin* with Nounish Red or Nounish Blue eyes, with a fun cc0 expansion pack to be enjoyed by all.

attributes.value: Licked - Don't Look in the Mirror
